<item>
            <title>[LU-19715] Provide Lustre version in lustreapi.h</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19715</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using &lt;tt&gt;lustreapi.h&lt;/tt&gt; to build tools outside the Lustre tree, it would helpful to know version of Lustre that is being used. This allows the tool to make compile time decisions on what&apos;s available in the Lustre version it&apos;s being built for.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One suggestion is to add &#160;&lt;tt&gt;lustre_version.h.in&lt;/tt&gt; and use&#160;subst to add the build version symbolically and &#160;as a string. &#160;The resulting file could be included by &lt;tt&gt;lustreapi.h&lt;/tt&gt;.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="94153">LU-19715</key>
            <summary>Provide Lustre version in lustreapi.h</summary>
